The paper deals with the problem of seed selection for viral marketing, which involves social influence and item inference. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). The paper also discusses data mining techniques for product recommendation, which falls under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). The paper also mentions e-commerce stores, which is related to cs.SOC (Social and Information Networks). The paper proposes a new model and algorithm, which involves computation and optimization, and hence, could be related to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
